Wani wakilin ɓangaren Wales na jam'iyyar Conservative ya ce ƙungiyarsa ta buɗe don canjin sunan, amma ya lura cewa furcin MWP yana kusa da kalmar Muppet, wanda a baya ga kasancewa sunan wasu shahararrun kayan ado, har ila yau, kalmar slang ce ta Burtaniya don Dust.
