Ya ce, rashin amincewar da 'yan sanda suka yi da shi abin fahimta ne.
Ya ce, "Mutane suna hulɗa da juna a wasu hanyoyi dabam dabam a yau".
Bar ba su zama wurin taruwa na al'umma ba, inda kowa yake zuwa kullum.
Amma game da Ikilisiyoyi, yana jin tsoro cewa kuɗin da aka samu daga sayar da dukiyar ba zai daɗe kamar yadda shugabannin suke tsammani ba.
Ya kara da cewa, ana iya maye gurbin majami'un da ke cike da mutanen da ba za su taimaka wa sauran wuraren ba.
Mafi yawan mutanen da ke sayen gidaje a cikin waɗannan gine-ginen za su kasance fararen fata, in ji shi,  sabili da haka kawai zai gaggauta ranar da waɗannan majami'u za su rufe ƙofofin su da kyau, saboda ba shi da wata ma'ana cewa yawancin waɗannan mutanen da ke shiga cikin waɗannan gidajen za su zama mambobi na waɗannan majami'u.
Dukansu biyu an gina su ne da fararen fata kafin Harlem ya zama baƙar fata Metropolitan Community a 1870 da St. Martin's shekaru goma daga baya.
Mutanen fararen fata na asali sun koma ƙasarsu a shekarun 1930.
Wani ɗan majami'ar baƙar fata wanda ya ci gaba da kasancewa a kusa da shi ya ɗauki ginin.
St. Martin's ta sami ikilisiyar baƙar fata a ƙarƙashin firist John Howard Johnson, wanda ya jagoranci wani ƙin yarda da masu ciniki a 125th Street  ɗaya daga cikin manyan 'yan kasuwa na Harlem  saboda sun ƙi yin aiki ko inganta baƙar fata.
Wani gobara a 1939 ya yi mummunan rauni ga ginin, kuma lokacin da mahaifin Johnson ya shirya shirin sake gina su suka sayi wani carillon.
Firist David Johnson, ɗan mahaifin Johnson kuma mai bin sa a St. Martin's, ya yi alfahari da cewa carillon ɗin shine kararrawar cocin talakawa.
Masanin da ya buga carillon a watan Yuli ya kira shi wani abu dabam: an al'adu da kuma  kayan aiki na tarihi.
Masanin, Tiffany Ng daga Jami'ar Michigan ya kuma lura cewa shi ne karillon na farko a duniya wanda wani ɗan baƙar fata mai suna Dionisio A. Lind ya buga, wanda ya ci gaba zuwa mafi girma a Riverside Church shekaru 18 da suka wuce.
A cewar Merriweather, St. Martin bai taba maye gurbinsa ba.
Abin da ya faru a St. Martin's a cikin watanni biyu na ƙarshe shine rikice-rikice tsakanin gine-gine da masu sana'a, wasu daga cikinsu sune jagorancin Ikilisiya da wasu daga bishopric.
Shugabancin Ikilisiyar, wanda ya ƙunshi layuka, ya rubuta wa bishop a watan Yuli game da damuwarsa cewa bishop din ya zo ya yi ƙoƙari ya tilasta farashin a kan cocin, duk da cewa cocin ba ya da hannu a cikin shigar da gine-ginen ko masu aikin da aka aiko da bishop.
Wasu 'yan majami'a sun yi korafi game da rashin nuna gaskiya daga bishopric.
Wani kifi mai suna shark ya ji wa wani ɗan shekara goma sha uku rauni a wani ruwa a California
Wani kifi mai suna shark ya kai hari kuma ya ji rauni a wani yaro mai shekaru 13 lokacin da ya zo California a ranar Asabar, ranar farko ta kakar wasan, a cewar hukumomi.
An kai harin ne kafin karfe 7:00 na safe a bakin rairayin bakin teku na Beacon a Encinitas.
Chad Hammel ya shaida wa KSWB-TV a San Diego cewa ya yi iyo tare da abokansa a cikin rabin sa'a a ranar Asabar da safe lokacin da ya ji yaron yana kira don taimako, kuma shi da wasu mutane sun yi iyo don fitar da yaron daga cikin ruwa.
A cewar Hammel, da farko ya yi tunanin cewa yaron ya yi kuka saboda farin cikin kama wani lobster, amma daga baya ya fahimci cewa yaron ya yi kuka 'An cije ni!
Na ciji!
Dukan ƙashin ƙashinsa ya rushe, in ji Hammel, wanda ya gano lalacewar lokacin da ya kai ga yaron.
"Na yi ihu cewa kowa ya fita daga cikin ruwan: 'Akwai kifi a cikin ruwa!'", in ji Hammel.
An kai yaron da motar daukar marasa lafiya zuwa asibitin Rady Children's Hospital da ke San Diego, inda yake cikin mawuyacin hali.
Ba a san irin kifin da ya kai harin ba.
Badevakt kyaftin Larry Giles ya ce a wani taron manema labarai cewa an ga wani shark a yankin makonni biyu da suka gabata, amma an tabbatar da cewa ba wani nau'in shark mai hatsari ba ne.
Giles ya kuma ce wanda aka kashe ya ji rauni sosai a jikinsa.
Hukumomi sun rufe hanyar daga Ponto Beach a Casablad zuwa Swami's a Ecinitas na tsawon sa'o'i 48 don dalilai na bincike da tsaro.
Giles ya lura cewa akwai fiye da 135 shark iri a yankin, amma mafi yawansu ba su da amfani.
Sainsbury's na shirin shiga kasuwar kula da kayan kwalliya ta Burtaniya
Sainsbury's yana kalubalantar Boots, Superdrug da Debenhams da kayan kwalliya da kayan kwalliya masu kama da kayan kwalliya, waɗanda ma'aikatan da aka horar da su musamman ke aiki.
Ana gwada ɗakunan da aka faɗaɗa a shaguna 11 a duk faɗin ƙasar a matsayin wani ɓangare na babbar hanyar shiga kasuwar kula da kayan kwalliya ta Burtaniya ta miliyan 2.8, wanda ke fuskantar ci gaba yayin da tallace-tallace na tufafi da kayan gida ke faɗuwa.
Kasuwancin kayan kwalliya na kayan kwalliya shine sakamakon ƙoƙarin da aka yi na neman sabon yanki don amfani da wurin da aka yi amfani da shi a baya don TVs, microwave da kayan gida.
