Shugaban Joko Widodo ya sanya ingantaccen tsarin samar da kayayyakin more rayuwa a Indonesia a matsayin babban batun yakin neman zabensa, kuma ya kashe kudi da yawa a kan hanya da jirgin kasa.
Amma rashin kuɗi ya kasance babbar matsala ga gwamnatin Joko, wanda za a sake zabarsa a shekara mai zuwa.
Shugaban Joko yana kuma fuskantar matsin lamba daga tsananin rikice-rikicen addini a Indonesia, inda mambobin musulmi suka koma ga addinin musulunci mai ra'ayin mazan jiya.
