Mutane sama da miliyan 20 ne suka kalli sauraron karar Brett Kavanaugh
Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shaidar da aka bayar a ranar Alhamis da aka rarraba a kan tashoshin talabijin shida, daga ɗan takarar majalisar dattijai Brett Kavanaugh da Christine Blasey Ford, matar da ta zarge shi da laifin cin zarafin mata da ya faru a shekarun 1980.
A halin yanzu, rikice-rikicen siyasa ya ci gaba, kuma masu watsa shirye-shiryen sun dakatar da wasikun da suke yi na yau da kullum don sanar da babban abin mamaki na ranar Jumma'a a cikin dakika na ƙarshe, lokacin da ya fito cewa sanatan Arizona, Jeff Flake, ya shirya don FBI ta gudanar da bincike na mako guda game da zargin.
Ford ta shaida wa majalisar dattijai cewa ta tabbata cewa wani ɗan giya ya yi mata fyade kuma ya yi ƙoƙari ya cire tufafinta a wani biki na makaranta.
A cikin shaidar sha'awar, Kavanaugh ya nace cewa ya tabbata kashi 100 cikin dari cewa wannan bai faru ba.
An yi tsammanin an ga wannan watsa shirye-shiryen a ranar Jumma'a fiye da miliyan 20.4 da Nielsen ya ruwaito.
Kamfanin ya lissafta matsakaicin yawan masu kallo don CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Masu kallo ba su da damar samun damar samun damar sauran cibiyoyin sadarwa da suka nuna sauraron, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Nielsen yana da matsala wajen auna masu amfani da ofis.
Don ba da hangen nesa, wannan adadi ne wanda ya dace da wasan karshe a gasar kwallon kafa ta Amurka ko Oscar.
Fox News Channel, wanda masu sauraro suka goyi bayan Kavanaugh tare da babbar sha'awa, ya jagoranci cibiyoyin sadarwa, tare da matsakaicin adadin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 don sauraron ranar, a cewar Nielsen.
ABC ita ce ta biyu tare da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS yana da miliyan 3.1, NBC yana da miliyan 2.94, MSNBC yana da miliyan 2.89 da CCNN yana da miliyan 2.52, a cewar Nielsen.
Har yanzu ana sha'awar sauraron karar.
Flake ne babban jarumin wasan kwaikwayon na ranar Juma'a.
A ranar Juma'a da safe, CNN da CBS sun yi fim dinsa yana kokarin hawa lif din zuwa wani taro a kotun yayin da masu zanga-zanga ke ihu da ihu a kansa.
Ya tsaya da kallon ido na tsawon minti da dama yayin da aka fitar da shi, yayin da aka watsa wannan lamarin kai tsaye a CNN.
"Ina tsaye a gabanka", wata mata ta ce.
