Guguwar Rosa ta yi barazanar Phoenix, Las Vegas, Salt Lake City da ambaliyar ruwa (yana iya zama mai kyau ga yankunan bushewa)
Wannan shi ne lokacin da za a yi wata guguwa mai zafi a Arizona, amma wannan zai faru a farkon mako mai zuwa, yayin da guguwar Rosa ta ci gaba da motsawa a cikin yankunan hamada a kudu maso yamma kuma ta haifar da ambaliyar ruwa.
Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta Kasa ta bayar da gargadin ambaliyar ruwa a ranar Litinin da Talata don yammacin Arizona da kuma kudu da gabashin Nevada, kudu maso gabashin California da Utah, ciki har da biranen Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas da Salt Lake City.
Ana sa ran cewa Rosa zai motsa a cikin madaidaiciyar layi ta hanyar Phoenix a ranar Talata, kuma ruwan sama zai fara yammacin ranar Litinin.
National Weather Service a Phoenix ya lura a Twitter cewa kawai 20 hadari sun ci gaba da kasancewa a matsayin hadari ko kuma low matsa lamba a cikin kilomita 320 na Phoenix tun 1950!
Katrina (1967) ta kasance guguwa har zuwa kilomita 65 daga iyakar zuwa Arizona.
Ƙididdigar National Hurricane Center ta ƙarshe ta nuna cewa ruwan sama ya kai 5  10 cm, har zuwa 15 cm a wasu wurare a Mongollon Rim a Arizona.
Sauran yankunan da ke cikin hamada a kudu maso yamma, ciki har da tsakiyar Rocky Mountains da Great Basin, za su iya samun tsakanin 2,5 da 5 cm, yayin da har zuwa 10 cm na ruwan sama zai yiwu a wasu yankuna.
Ga waɗanda ba su cikin haɗarin ambaliyar ruwa, Rosa na iya zama albarka, tun da yankin yana fama da fari.
Ko da yake ambaliyar ruwa matsala ce mai tsanani, wasu daga cikin wannan ruwan sama zai iya zama da amfani, tun da yake kudu maso yammacin Amurka a halin yanzu yana cikin yanayin fari.
A cewar United States Drought Monitor, sama da kashi 40 cikin dari na Arizona suna fuskantar matsanancin fari, wanda shine na biyu mafi girma, a cewar weather.com.
Da farko guguwar Rosa ta sauka a tsibirin Baja California na ƙasar Mexico.
Rosa har yanzu yana da ƙarfin guguwa a ranar Lahadi da safe, tare da ƙarfin iska mafi girma a 137 km, yana da nisan kilomita 620 daga Punta Eugenia a Mexico kuma yana motsawa 19 km / h.
Guguwar tana fuskantar ruwan sanyi a cikin Tekun Fasifik, kuma tana rasa ƙarfi.
Saboda haka ana tsammanin zai buge Mexico da karfin guguwa a ranar Litinin da yamma ko yamma.
Ruwan sama a wasu sassan Mexico na iya zama mai ƙarfi kuma yana haifar da babbar ambaliyar ruwa.
Total ruwan sama na 7,5 15 cm ana tsammanin daga Baja California zuwa arewa maso yammacin Sonora, tare da damar har zuwa 25 cm na ruwan sama, a cewar weather.com.
Rosa za ta ci gaba da motsawa a arewacin Mexico a matsayin hadari na tropical har sai ta kai iyakar Arizona a farkon ranar Talata da safe a matsayin wani ƙananan zafi, wanda ya ci gaba da motsawa ta hanyar Arizona da kuma kudancin Utah a cikin yammacin ranar Talata.
Babban hatsarin da ake tsammanin daga Rosa ko ragowar shi yana da tsananin ruwan sama a Baja California, arewa maso yammacin Sonora da kuma kudu maso yammacin hamada a Amurka, a cewar National Hurricane Center.
Ana sa ran wannan ruwan zai haifar da ambaliyar ruwa da ruwa da sauri a cikin hamada da kuma ƙasa a cikin tsaunuka.
