Ya kamata Amurka ta ninka tallafinta ga AI
Yayin da kasar Sin ke kara samun ci gaba a fannin kere-kere, Amurka ta kamata ta ninka yawan kudaden da take kashewa wajen bincike a wannan fannin, a cewar Kai Fu Lee, mai zuba jari kuma mai amfani da kere-kere, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Wannan magana ta zo ne bayan da wasu sassan gwamnatin Amurka suka zo da sanarwar game da ilimin kere kere, duk da cewa Amurka gabaɗaya ba ta da tsarin dabarun kere kere.
China, a nata bangaren, ta gabatar da wani shiri a bara, da nufin zama ta daya a fannin kirkire-kirkire na wucin gadi nan da shekarar 2030.
"Samun karin kudi biyu a fannin bincike kan kere-kere zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, tunda duk sauran kasashen duniya sun yi nisa a baya da Amurka, kuma muna neman babbar nasara ta gaba", in ji Lee.
"Samun tallafi sau biyu na iya ninka yiwuwar samun babban ci gaba a fannin kere kere daga Amurka", in ji Lee a wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon.
