Lokacin taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaban kasa zai fara taron zaben mutane da yawa a wannan yammacin a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin taron jama'a biyar da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da wuraren da ya tsaya a biranen da ke da goyon baya sosai, kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yanzu da aka saita zaben tabbatar da zaɓaɓɓen ɗan takararsa na babban kotu, Trump yana da burin samun goyon baya ga zaɓen da ke tafe, tun da yake 'yan Republican suna cikin haɗarin rasa iko a kan majalisa lokacin da masu jefa kuri'a suka je zauren zabe a watan Nuwamba.
Yaushe ne taron Trump na yammacin Virginia zai gudana a daren yau, kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon sa a yanar gizo?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia zai fara ne da karfe 19 na yammacin yau Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a ƙasa ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Ana sa ran Trump zai tattauna batun sauraron karar da aka yi wa Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka zargi da cin zarafin mata, a wannan makon.
Babban manufar taron shine tallafawa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar babban zabe a watan Nuwamba.
A sakamakon haka, Shugaba Trump ya ce waɗannan taron jama'a guda biyar da za a yi a cikin makonni masu zuwa suna da burin tayar da masu ba da agaji da masu tallafawa yayin da 'yan Republican ke ƙoƙarin karewa da faɗaɗa mafi rinjaye da suke da su a majalisar dattijai da majalisar wakilai, a cewar Reuters.
Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandarsa, shugaban zai je jihohi da dama kamar yadda zai iya yayin da muke fuskantar wani babban yakin neman zabe, in ji wani mai gabatar da jawabi ga Trump wanda ya nemi a sakaya sunansa.
Taron na yamma, wanda a cewar shirin zai faru a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, zai iya jan hankalin 'yan wasan daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, kuma Pittsburgh-pressen zai rufe shi, a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai ziyarci jihar West Virginia a karo na biyu a cikin watan da ya gabata, jihar da ya lashe da kashi 40 cikin dari a 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ya yi kasa a kan binciken.
Alamar da ta dace ga Morrisey ita ce shugaban ya zo ya yi kokarin kara masa karfin gwiwa a zaben da aka yi a shekarar da ta gabata, in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
