Jaridar ta ce, an shirya sabon jirgin ruwan Jamus a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen yakin da aka yi a lokacin yakin basasa, amma hakan ba zai faru ba sai a farkon shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin tsarin aiki da kuma tsadar aiki, kamar yadda kafofin yada labarai na gida suka ruwaito.
An kammala aikin Rheinland-Pfalz, jirgin saman sabbin jirage na Baden-Wuerttemberg, yanzu an sanya shi zuwa farkon rabin 2019, a cewar jaridar Die Zeit wanda ya ambaci wani jami'in soja.
An ba da jirgin ruwa a 2014, amma manyan matsalolin da aka samu bayan bayarwa sun ci gaba da aikin.
Jirgin ruwa huɗu na Baden-Wuerttemberg-class da aka ba da umarnin gaba ɗaya a shekara ta 2007, za su maye gurbin tsoffin jirage na Bremen-class.
An amince da su da za a yi amfani da su da babbar makami, da wasu antiluftskyts da antiskips missiles da kuma wasu fasaha na stealth, irin su rage radar, infrar red da kuma siginar sauti.
Sauran muhimman halaye sun haɗa da tsawon lokaci na kiyayewa  ya kamata ya yiwu a yi amfani da sababbin jiragen ruwa har zuwa shekaru biyu daga tashar jiragen ruwa.
Duk da haka, jinkirin da ake yi yana nufin cewa jiragen ruwa masu tasowa  da aka ce su ba Jamus ƙarfin teku  sun riga sun kasance a cikin aikin, in ji Die Zeit.
F125-fregatten mai haɗari ya haifar da sanarwa a bara, lokacin da sojojin Jamus suka ƙi su sa jirgin cikin aiki kuma suka mayar da shi zuwa tashar Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da sojojin suka mayar da jirgin ruwa ga wani mai gina jirgi bayan an kawo shi.
Ba a san dalilin dawowar ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ambaci wasu muhimman bayanai da suka sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani a wani aikin yaki.
Abubuwan da aka tsara na software sun kasance masu mahimmanci tun lokacin da jirgin ruwa a Baden-Wuerttemberg-klass ya kamata a yi aiki da wani ma'aikaci na kimanin 120 - kawai rabin rabin ma'aikatan tsofaffin jiragen ruwa a Bremen-klass.
An kuma gano cewa jirgin yana da nauyin nauyi mai yawa, wanda ke rage ƙarfinsa kuma yana iyakance damar da ke cikin jirgin don yin haɓaka a nan gaba.
An kiyasta nauyin "Rheinland-Pfalz" mai nauyin 7000-tonn ya zama nauyin nauyin jirgin ruwa guda ɗaya wanda Jamus ta yi amfani da shi a yakin duniya na biyu.
