Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 aka kashe a wata girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na kasar a ranar Juma'a, a cewar jami'an kasar, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Sadarwar ta fita daga aiki, kuma ma'aikatan ceto ba su iya samun bayanai daga Donggala regentship ba, wani yanki a arewacin Palu wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5.
A Palu, an yi watsi da mutane fiye da 16 000 bayan bala'in ya auku.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birni ne na lardin Sulawesi, wanda ke ƙarshen bakin teku mai zurfi a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan jama'a 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Birnin ya yi bikin shekaru 40 da haihuwa lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka faru.
Donggala wani yanki ne mai nisan kilomita 300 a arewa maso yammacin Sulawesi.
Regentship, wani yanki ne na yanki a ƙarƙashin matakin lardin, yana da yawan jama'a 299 200 a cikin 2017.
Kifi da noma sune abubuwan da ke haifar da tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala.
Nikkelgruvedrift ma yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma an mayar da hankali ne a Morowali, a bakin tekun da ke gaba da Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sami tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar hukumar agajin gaggawa ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Wani tsunami ya kuma afkawa yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996 inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana kan girgizar ƙasa a cikin Tekun Pacific kuma ana fuskantar ta a kai a kai ta hanyar girgizar ƙasa.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a yammacin gabar lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226 000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Wata babbar girgizar ƙasa ta auku a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 6.8 ta auku a kudancin Java, tsibirin da ke da yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ta haifar da tsunami da ya auku a gabar teku.
2009: An yi wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.6 a kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane sama da 1100 aka kashe.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta auku a tsibirin Mentawai, a wajen Sumatra, kuma ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa ta girgiza yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh kuma ta haifar da lalacewa da firgici yayin da ake tuna wa mutane game da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a 2004.
Ba a haifar da tsunami ba a wannan lokacin, amma sama da 100 sun mutu daga gine-gine masu haɗuwa.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta auku a tsibirin Lombok na ƙasar Indonesia, ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, yawancinsu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasa ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta haifar da dubban masu yawon bude ido da aka yi wa ragowar.
