Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu bayan da wata girgizar kasa ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi na kasar Indonesiya a ranar Juma'a.
Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta haifar da tsunami kuma ta lalata dubban gidaje.
Wutar lantarki da hanyoyin sadarwa sun ragu, kuma ana sa ran yawan mutuwar zai karu a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
Girgizar ta auku ne a yankin Sulawesi da ke arewa maso gabashin babban birnin kasar Indonesia, wato Jakarta.
Ana yada bidiyon a shafukan sada zumunta da ke nuna barkewar cutar.
Mutane ɗarurruwa sun taru don bikin bakin teku a birnin Palu lokacin da tsunami ya yi tahowar ruwa.
Hukumomin tarayya na neman hukuncin kisa kan wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York
Hukumomin da ke da alhakin cin zarafin mutane a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da aikata ta'addanci a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas  hukuncin da ba a yi amfani da shi ba a jihar don aikata laifi tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekaru 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya daga Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a kan West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya yi wa masu tafiya da keke a kan hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, dole ne mai gabatar da kara ya tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe wadanda aka kashe takwas ainihin  kuma ya haifar da mummunan lalacewar jiki tare da niyya, a cewar sanarwar niyyar neman hukuncin kisa a Southern District of New York.
Duk waɗannan abubuwan suna da damar yanke hukuncin kisa, a cewar takardar shari'ar.
Makonni da yawa bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta jefa zargin da aka yi wa Saipov, tare da wasu laifuka takwas na kisan kai da ke da alaƙa da karɓar kuɗi, a fuskar Saipov, wanda ake amfani da shi ta hanyar hukumomin tarayya a cikin al'amuran aikata laifuka, da kuma zargin tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Wannan harin ya bukaci ƙaddara da niyya, in ji mai gabatar da kara, wanda ya bayyana yadda Saipov ya yi shi a matsayin mugu, mai zalunci da lalacewa.
Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da raunin mutane, dukiya da asarar dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco, ya tabbatar da sanarwar game da niyya.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma sun shude tun lokacin da gundumar kudancin New York ta gabatar da shari'ar da za ta iya yanke hukuncin kisa.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa kan masu sayar da miyagun kwayoyi biyu, amma an yanke masa hukuncin rai da rai a kurkuku a watan Satumbar 2009.
A baya can an yanke hukuncin kisa a cikin wani shari'ar tarayya a New York, a 1953 ne Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa don yin leken asiri ga Sovietuniyon a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe Rosenberg-ma'aurata a cikin kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, daga Uzbekistan, bai nuna nadama ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun shari'a.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa yana farin ciki da abin da ya yi.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomin cewa an yi wahayi zuwa gare shi don kai harin bayan da ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayar hannu, a cewar mai laifin.
Ya kuma nemi a rataye tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya bayyana kansa ba shi da laifi bayan da aka tuhume shi da abubuwa 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin masu kare Saipov da aka zaba a fili, ya ce sun yi takaici game da shawarar da aka yanke.
"Mun yi imanin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar ikirari da kuma zaman gidan yari har abada ba tare da samun damar sakin ba, zai kara wa duk wanda abin ya shafa rauni", in ji Patton.
Saipov ya bukaci jami'an tsaro da su daina neman hukuncin kisa.
'Yan majalisar dokokin Tory sun ce ya kamata Nigel FARAGE ya dauki nauyin tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin mobilising sojojin mutane a yau a wani zanga-zanga a lokacin taron Tory.
Tsohon shugaban Ukip ya ce 'yan siyasa za su ji matsin lamba daga 'yan gurguzu lokacin da wani dan majalisar dokokin Theresa May ya ce shi ne zai jagoranci tattaunawar da EU.
Mai tsaron baya Peter Bone ya gaya wa masu zanga-zangar a Birmingham cewa Birtaniya  za ta kasance an yanke ta yanzu idan Farage ya kasance sakataren Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da May ke fuskanta na sasanta tsakanin bangarorin da suka rabu, ya kara da cewa 'yan Tories masu goyon bayan ci gaba da zama a majalisar dokoki sun halarci zanga-zangar nuna adawa da ficewar Birtaniya daga EU a birnin.
Firaministan na fafutukar tabbatar da shirinsa na Brexit a kan hanya don ya tsayayya wa hare-haren Brexiteers, Remainers da EU.
Masu goyon bayanta sun nace cewa za ta ci gaba da ƙoƙarin samun yarjejeniya da Brüssel duk da komawar da ta yi da kuma tilasta wa masu shakkar Turai da Labour su zabi tsakanin fakinta da kaos.
Bone ya gaya wa masu zanga-zangar a Solihull cewa yana son ya yi watsi da shirin Brexit.
Ya ba da shawarar cewa ya kamata a sanya Farage a matsayin memba kuma ya sami alhakin tattaunawar da Brüssel.
Ya ce, "Idan shi ne ke da alhakin, da mun fita yanzu".
Dan majalisar Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: "Zan goyi bayan Brexit, amma dole ne mu yi watsi da shirin Brexit".
Lokacin da yake bayyana yadda yake adawa da Tarayyar Turai, ya ce: "Ba mu yi yaƙi a yaƙe-yaƙe biyu na duniya don zama masu biyayya ba.
Muna so mu yi dokokinmu a kasarmu.
Bone ya musanta zargin cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya canza tun lokacin da aka kada kuri'ar a 2016: "Gaskiyar cewa mutanen Burtaniya sun canza ra'ayi kuma suna son kasancewa a cikin EU, ba daidai ba ne.
Tory Brexiteer Andrea Jenkyns ma ta halarci zanga-zangar kuma ta gaya wa manema labarai: Ina cewa a sauƙaƙe: Ministan ƙasa, saurari mutane.
Shirin Brexit ba shi da kyau a idon jama'a. 'Yan adawa ba za su kada kuri'a a kansa ba. Ba shi da kyau a idon jam'iyyarmu da kuma 'yan gwagwarmayarmu, wadanda a zahiri su ne ke birgima kan tituna kuma su zabe mu a zagaye na farko.
Ku yi watsi da shirin Brexit ku fara sauraro.
A cikin sakon kai tsaye zuwa ga May, ta kara da cewa: Ministocin kasa suna rike da aikin idan sun cika alkawuransu.
Farage ya bayyana cewa 'yan siyasa za su sami ji matsin lamba idan suna tunanin cin amanar shawarar da aka yanke a zaben 2016.
Ya ce, "Wannan batun amincewa ne tsakaninmu, tsakanin jama'a da kuma 'yan siyasa".
Suna kokarin cin amanar Brexit, kuma muna nan a yau don sanar da su cewa ba za su samu damar yin hakan ba.
A wani sako da ya aika wa masu sauraro, ya kara da cewa: "Ina so ku bar 'yan siyasarmu, wadanda ke kan hanyar cin amanar Brexit, su ji matsin lamba.
Muna tattara sojojin jama'a a wannan kasa da ta ba mu nasara a Brexit kuma ba za mu huta ba har sai mun zama mai zaman kanta, mai cin gashin kanta, mai alfahari da Burtaniya.
A halin yanzu, Remainers sun yi tafiya ta Birmingham kafin su yi taron siyasa na tsawon sa'o'i biyu a tsakiyar birnin.
Wasu 'yan gwagwarmaya sun yi amfani da tutar Tories Against Brexit bayan kaddamar da kungiyar a karshen mako.
Wani memba na Labour Lord Adonis ya yi ba'a ga masu ra'ayin mazan jiya saboda matsalolin tsaro da suke da shi tare da wani ɓangare na taron yayin da taron ya fara.
"Waɗannan su ne mutanen da ke gaya mana cewa za su iya samun tsarin IT da duk fasahar da za ta iya ba Kanada da ƙari, ƙari, don iyakar da ba ta da matsala, don cinikayya ba tare da iyaka ba a Ireland", in ji shi.
