Warren yana tunanin gaske don tsayawa a matsayin dan takarar shugaban kasa
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta Amurka ta ce za ta yi la'akari da gaske don zama dan takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa dan jam'iyyar Democrat daga Massachusetts ya yi magana game da nan gaba a wani taron majalisar dattijai a yammacin Massachusetts a ranar Asabar.
Warren, mai yawan sukar shugaban kasa Donald Trump, yana neman sake zaben a watan Nuwamba a kan wakilin jam'iyyar Republican Geoff Diehl, wanda shi ne mataimakin shugaban Trump a Massachusetts a shekarar 2016.
Ta kasance a tsakiyar jita-jita game da ko za ta yi hamayya da Trump a 2020.
Taron ranar Asabar da yamma a Holyoke shine taron ta na 36 tare da masu jefa kuri'a, waɗanda suka yi amfani da tsarin majalisar tun lokacin da Trump ya zama shugaban kasa.
