Patrick Dwyer ya ci wa Giants kwallo biyu a wasan da suka yi da Dundee
Dundee Stars sun yi wasan karshe a wasan da suka yi a ranar Juma'a a gasar Elite League da Belfast Giants ta hanyar lashe wasan da suka buga 5-3 a Dundee a ranar Asabar.
Giants sun samu jagorancin kai hari ta hanyar harbi daga Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun daidaita wa 'yan wasan gida kafin Dwyer ya sake dawo da jagorancin Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya daidaita wa Dundee kafin kwallo biyu da Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya zira ya tabbatar da nasarar.
Wannan shine karo na uku da 'yan wasan Adam Keefe suka yi a gasar Elite League, bayan da suka doke Dundee 2-1 a Belfast a ranar Juma'a da yamma.
Wannan shi ne karo na uku da suka yi a kakar wasa ta bana, kuma Giants sun lashe wasannin da suka gabata guda uku.
Dwyer ya buɗe wasan a minti na hudu a 3:35 tare da taimakon Kendall McFaull, kuma David Rutherford ya buga wasan lokacin da Beauvillier ya ninka jagorancin minti hudu daga baya.
A cikin abin da ya zama lokacin buɗewa mai ban tsoro, Sullivan ya jagoranci ƙungiyar gida a wasan a 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya tashi zuwa daidaitawar Cownies a 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da cewa Giants suna da jagorancin hutu lokacin da ya ɗauki burin sa na biyu a ƙarshen farkon.
Kungiyar ta sake komawa kuma Bouchard ya daidaita sau ɗaya tare da burin wasan kwaikwayo a 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun tafi tare don taimakawa Nielsen ya ba Dundee jagorancin farko a lokacin wasan a ƙarshen rabi na biyu, kuma ya tabbatar da nasara tare da fifth a rabi a cikin ƙarshen.
Giants, wanda yanzu ya rasa hudu daga cikin wasanni biyar da suka gabata, suna wasa a gida da Milton Keynes a wasan su na gaba a ranar Juma'a.
