Team Europe ta lashe gasar Ryder ta 2018 bayan ta doke Team Amurka da sakamakon karshe na 16.5 da 10.5 a Le Golf National a wajen Paris, Faransa.
Yanzu Amurka ta rasa sau shida bayan juna a Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake samun kursiyin lokacin da aka yi wa dan wasan Denmark Thomas Bjørn 14,5 maki da suke bukata don doke Amurka.
Tauraron Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya yi fama da manyan sassan gasar, ya yi wasan sa a cikin ruwa a rami na 16, kuma ya ga Francesco Molinari ya doke shi.
