Rahoton da aka bayar kwanan nan daga Hukumar Kula da Kifi da Kiwo ta Florida (FWC) ya nuna raguwar yawan ruwan teku a yankunan Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, an ba da rahoton cewa akwai wasu furanni masu haske a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier County  wanda ke nuna raguwar yawan.
Wani furen ruwan ja yana da nisan kilomita 210 a gabar tekun, daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudu a Lee County.
An gano wasu wurare a kusa da kilomita 16 a gefen gabar teku na Hillsborough County, amma a wurare da yawa fiye da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da algae a Pasco County.
